item.title: Was the Sprint Race the best part of the weekend? - 2023 F1 Austrian Grand Prix Review
item.description:
The 2023 F1 Austrian Grand Prix was the second sprint weekend of the season, and a lot of people said the Sprint race was far better than the actual race. Verstappen won again (shock), and the Ferrari's actually looked good for a change. 

Enjoy The WTF1 Post race podcast hosted by Harry Benjamin with special guests Nicola Hume and Antonia Rankin, as they review the 2023 Austrian GP.
